{"tid":874449,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[挪威神劇] SKAM (羞恥)","createTime":"2018-10-24T08:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T10:58:10.000Z","uid":76777,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"132c589570a56b6d59f12f6da5583f7c87d8c810","tid":874449,"uid":76777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.paulette-magazine.com/assets/wysiwyg/5932-skam-streaming-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.paulette-magazine.com%2Fassets%2Fwysiwyg%2F5932-skam-streaming-01.jpg&h=367e21aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n號稱全挪威、甚至全北歐最多人睇過嘅電視劇<br />\n<br />\n劇情圍繞一班挪威學生嘅校園生活，總共四季，每季都會喺主要角色裡面揀一位做主角:<br />\n<br />\n第一季: 主角Amy同男朋友Jonas嘅感情、同姊妹團磨合<br />\n<br />\n第二季: 姊妹團其中一員Noora同學校 &rdquo;不良分子&rdquo; William嘅感情發展<br />\n<br />\n第三季: Jonas兄弟幫其中一員Isak出柜過程<br />\n<br />\n第四季: 姊妹團其中一員 身為穋斯林嘅Sana如何克服現代文化同信仰產生嘅衝突<br />\n<br />\n劇入面涉及好多議題，宗教信仰、性取向、性侵、欺凌等等都有，但會順住劇情自然帶出，完全唔悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNoora 勁有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://amuse-images.vice.com/wp_upload/2017/02/Skam-3-13-@-Skam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Famuse-images.vice.com%2Fwp_upload%2F2017%2F02%2FSkam-3-13-%40-Skam.jpg&h=3be4239b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暖男 Isak <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://files.baaam.se/uploads/sites/36/fly-images/44603/Skam-Isak-1-1280x667-c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.baaam.se%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F36%2Ffly-images%2F44603%2FSkam-Isak-1-1280x667-c.jpg&h=740709f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺度推介下 等多啲人知道呢套劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f831572462df36c41c25246b6d327062c75795c","tid":874449,"uid":156160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"偶然睇左SKAM之後就沉淪左落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Isak Even第三季甜到核爆、Sana女皇第四季以為朋友都嫌棄佢點知原來全部人都原諒左佢仲用新車迎接佢個幕爆喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddaa914cefd657eddadbdfaf1a4f9b55cfde2c8f","tid":874449,"uid":156160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"估唔到巴打都會睇！真心希望更多人認識呢套劇，睇完真係會反思好多人性同人際關係既野，同埋你所講果嗰同性戀、宗教議題等等"},{"pid":"921df81bab09f05edf28fbe7cc67ffcebae9347f","tid":874449,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T18:28:31.000Z","msg":"仆街 一早睇左<br />\n而家出緊法國版，<br />\n只睇左第三輯，覺得同原版一樣咁好睇。<br />\n不過因為重睇同樣劇情<br />\n我覺得我終於明個種好複雜嘅情緒<br />\n所以某啲位覺得比原版更好睇。"},{"pid":"fad3bc85a64da479fdd3d465f54a899cc10f88bb","tid":874449,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T18:34:03.000Z","msg":"S1講eating disorder個到好撚入心<br />\nS3講失眠都覺得好有代入感<br />\n<br />\n每一幕都輕輕帶過，但又好明白同會思考佢地想表達咩。好簡單但又易明又易代入。好好睇"},{"pid":"52937e1d0e7591030e296e61af7246e622a99a94","tid":874449,"uid":38071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"好多個parallel universe嘅skam同時發生緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追緊druck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5f10e8a9ecca2914589cb6067f67fa5b937482","tid":874449,"uid":57576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"921df81bab09f05edf28fbe7cc67ffcebae9347f","tid":874449,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T18:28:31.000Z","msg":"仆街 一早睇左<br />\n而家出緊法國版，<br />\n只睇左第三輯，覺得同原版一樣咁好睇。<br />\n不過因為重睇同樣劇情<br />\n我覺得我終於明個種好複雜嘅情緒<br />\n所以某啲位覺得比原版更好睇。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:11:53.000Z","msg":"法版第三季超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得佢對躁鬱症嘅描寫做得比原版更好，但當然原版地位係無可替代嘅